    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to confirm its mechanical integrity and roadworthiness. The exterior maintains a distinguished presence, complemented by a well-preserved interior that reflects a high standard of previous ownership. This offering provides a sophisticated driving experience for those who prioritize reliability and proven maintenance history. Service documentation is available to verify its consistent upkeep.",
