    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-loved, perfect for anyone looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken care of the essentials, so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat and show you around the vehicle!",
