    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable and well-presented daily driver. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch, consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains smoke-free and exceptionally clean. The leather seating is soft and free of cracks or bolster wear, while the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats. All electronic components, including the touchscreen infotainment, heated seats, and driver-assist sensors, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has been maintained on a strict schedule with full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The engine runs smoothly without any unusual noises, and the transmission provides crisp, effortless shifts. The tires are matching sets with significant tread depth remaining, and the brake pads were recently replaced. This car drives straight and true, offering a quiet and comfortable ride that belies its mileage. Complete service history and two sets of keys are included.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been maintained to rigorous standards to ensure a seamless blend of performance and long-term reliability. It features a refined interior and a commanding presence on the road, representing a premier opportunity for the discerning driver who prioritizes mechanical integrity and aesthetic sophistication. This is a professionally vetted asset ready for immediate acquisition.",
