    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my awesome car! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in great shape, perfect for someone who wants a solid ride without the brand-new price tag. It runs beautifully and has plenty of life left for all your road trips and daily commutes. I've taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 29500.0,
