    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response and a linear power band. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory variable M-differential. Mechanical integrity is prioritized; the VANOS system has been recently shimmed and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to maintain chassis rigidity against torsional stress. Riding on a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, the handling remains sharp and predictable. This is a mechanically sound driver's car, showing minor patina consistent with use but optimized for peak performance.",
